63
00:09:01,709 --> 00:09:06,308
輝きは君の中に
Brightness is inside of you

64
00:09:17,205 --> 00:09:23,125
楽しいことでも 毎日続いたら
Even fun things, if they continue every day

65
00:09:23,845 --> 00:09:29,925
