140
00:17:27,503 --> 00:17:30,093
Oh baby I can't stop my love for you

141
00:17:30,093 --> 00:17:34,413
君のすべてになってね
Be my everything.

142
00:17:34,413 --> 00:17:43,303
繋いだ手信じて　歩いてゆくと誓うよ
Believing in our joined hands, I vow to walk on.

143
