148
00:18:38,413 --> 00:18:42,013
誓い合ったなぐさめ合った
...we made vows and comforted each other.

149
00:18:42,213 --> 00:18:49,293
もう恋は二度としないよって
Saying we'd never fall in love again.

150
00:18:50,193 --> 00:18:53,993
そんな強い結束は形を変え
That strong bond has changed its form...

151
00:18:53,993 --> 00:18:57,513
今じゃこんなに逞しい私達の
...to our current, resilient...

152
00:18:57,513 --> 00:19:04,003
ライフスタイル エブリディ エブリタイム
...lifestyle, every day, every time.

153
00:19:06,193 --> 00:19:09,513
頬寄せ合って写る写真の笑顔に
In the smiles of the photos taken with cheeks together...

154
00:19:09,513 --> 00:19:17,813
少しの寂しさ詰め込んで
...I packed a little bit of loneliness.

155
00:19:22,283 --> 00:19:25,593
潔く カッコよく 明日からは
Purely and coolly, from tomorrow...

156
00:19:25,593 --> 00:19:29,113
誰もが振り向く女になる
...I'll become a woman everyone turns to look at.

157
00:19:29,393 --> 00:19:33,283
たとえ二人離ればなれになっても
Even if we two are pulled apart...

158
00:19:33,283 --> 00:19:36,913
心はずっと一緒に
...our hearts will always be together.

159
00:20:01,290 --> 00:20:02,490
...いられないね
...can't stay as you are.

160
00:20:02,790 --> 00:20:06,390
若い子みんなそうだと 思われるのは
I don't like it when people think
all young kids are like that.

161
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:10,790
不本意で どうしようもないじゃない
It's so frustrating and there's nothing I can do.

162
00:20:13,090 --> 00:20:14,490
でもね
But you know...

163
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:19,290
私たち友達のこと 何より大切にしてる
We treasure our friends more than anything else.

164
00:20:19,690 --> 00:20:23,790
きっと大人よりも
Even more than adults, I'm sure.

165
00:20:29,690 --> 00:20:33,690
夢を見て 涙して 傷ついても
Even if we dream, cry, and get hurt...

166
00:20:33,690 --> 00:20:37,790
現実は がむしゃらに来るし
Reality comes at us relentlessly.

167
00:20:37,990 --> 00:20:42,490
自分の居場所 存在価値は 失くせない
We can't lose our place or the value of our existence.

168
